==English==
===Noun phrase===
'''[[storage]] [[organ]]''' (''plural'' '''storage organs''')

#{{botany}} A part of a plant, such as a [[bulb]], specifically modified for storage of energy (generally in the form of [[carbohydrate]]s) or of water.

